wiki.summary: In this heartfelt song, Polo G relates his current relationship with his girlfriend to Martin and Gina, a couple within the 1990s TV sitcom Martin. Dropping references to designer clothes and expensive items, he boasts about how he’s improved his girl’s lifestyle – and how she’s made everything better for him. “Martin & Gina” was certified platinum by the RIAA on October 29th, 2020. Read more on Last.fm.
